{"tid":30998,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夜市上廁所遭性侵　6歲女童驚逃畫面曝光","createTime":"2016-12-09T12:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T21:49:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ca8857ae2c2fdf9fdcf482d5b9be419c907612e","tid":30998,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:02:43.000Z","msg":"屏東南州傳出6歲女童遭性侵案件！一名就讀國小的6歲女童，昨（8日）晚到南州夜市找擺攤的父親，晚間6時許，女童到夜市附近的代天府公廁上廁所，疑似遭一名之前就埋伏在廁所內的歹徒性侵，女童父親後來發現，帶女童到警局報案，涉案嫌犯疑似為當地人士，因自知難逃法網，昨晚主動向警方投案。<br />\n<br />\n這起疑似性侵案引發各方關注，警方調閱公廁附近監視器，發現女童於晚上6點41分獨自一人上廁所，進廁所前還開心跑跑跳跳，但嫌疑人尾隨在後，約於6點42分鬼祟進入廁所，在廁所前還左右張望。在監視器無法監控的廁所內，女童疑遭侵犯，尖叫求救，引起附近民眾驚慌，女童父親驚覺拿木棍趕到廁所，父女兩人於7點3分快跑離開廁所，嫌犯則轉身跳離竄逃，情況緊急。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，被害女童父親當場發現嫌疑人惡行，一度還發生扭打，但被嫌疑人趁亂逃逸，警方根據目擊者轉述，鎖定嫌疑人，男子才在友人陪同下投案。<br />\n<br />\n（李易親／屏東報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161209/420_d1d61f53fec7a38555ef293fc0744146.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161209%2F420_d1d61f53fec7a38555ef293fc0744146.jpg&h=ff139bd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女童尖叫求救，與趕來救援的父親跑離現場。翻攝畫面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161209/420_814bf6739445aacaa8543a274732b2d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161209%2F420_814bf6739445aacaa8543a274732b2d4.jpg&h=fa28cc99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女童遭性侵的案發公廁。李易親攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161209/420_c48558c330343a66c7ea38078a4dd3cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161209%2F420_c48558c330343a66c7ea38078a4dd3cf.jpg&h=e4b3e30d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女童與趕來救援的父親跑離現場。翻攝畫面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161209/420_f4b7c1c6b765e62741347835b05e7695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161209%2F420_f4b7c1c6b765e62741347835b05e7695.jpg&h=f67d6bed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嫌犯尾隨在廁所埋伏畫面曝光。翻攝畫面"},{"pid":"409f7578c5fb7e3077113e4f9462cf23fe11a572","tid":30998,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n強國"},{"pid":"0c611196cff9f45923d797b7c6a3ae693a54767f","tid":30998,"uid":59830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:09:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09daeb682e9d16ebfc428c6aba30af93f37d702a","tid":30998,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:17:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n強國</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係台灣咩？"},{"pid":"257d23e6c43dbb0e885caa2a0ff6b953090e9c5c","tid":30998,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:21:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n強國</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係真屈機男黎<br />\n無見一排柒左咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ddeff7a16634ca86b19e86ca6669a91f477c47","tid":30998,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T21:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}